data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
1. All information that you view on Protea must at all times be kept in strict confidentiality.
2. Student photos, student personal details, medical info, disciplinary information, academic results, etc may not be copied or distributed to any individual or organization other than the student to whom these details belong.
3. Sub-Wardens are treated as members of staff, and if they breach the rules above they will be held accountable through the staff disciplinary code at Rhodes University.
4. You may not make your protea login/student number and password available to anyone else.
5. You must abide by the Acceptable User Policy of the Rhodes University IT Division.
